{"title":"友谊","authors":["任丹"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":2,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"友谊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任丹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏联同志鲍里斯·库巴列夫在靠近中国边境的地方放牧，在暴风雪里他迷了路，走到中国境内，冻倒在地上……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫天的大风雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处一片迷茫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的同志呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么躺在地上？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里是医院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屋内好像春天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝杯牛奶吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快恢复强健。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们没见过面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是并不陌生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像多年老友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像亲生弟兄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒冷莫过风雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友谊却比火热；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再见呵同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问候你的亲人。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}